cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.NE 

The paper is about meta-learning for few-shot learning, which is a topic that falls under the intersection of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses domain adaptation (cs.CL) and knowledge distillation (cs.NE) as strategies to improve few-shot learning, which further supports the likelihood of these sub-categories.
